sentence: Tuesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 6,737.87.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 2.05 billion.
Declining stocks led advancers by 1.24 to 1 ratio.
There were 1333 advancers and 1652 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 32 stocks reached a 52 week high and 57 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed down -.36% for the day; a total of -22.54 points.
JD.com, Inc. ( JD ) had the largest percent change down (-5.9%) while Vodafone Group Plc ( VOD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 5.63%.
The Dow Jones index closed down -.13% for the day; a total of -30.23 points.
General Electric Company ( GE ) had the largest percent change down (-5.89%) while Home Depot, Inc. (The) ( HD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 1.64%.
